RACE_DESERTROCK_UNREAL TOTALLY REMADE BY UNREA1
AtentionThis map has been fixed for the latest rallyrace available mod fixed by Natalya. 25-11-2010
So... Why did I decide to remake race_desertrock? - It didn't look good; - walls intercepting; - it had a huge bug, that allowed some people to finish the map in almost half the time it should be. _ Map info: - big - 3 laps - env_sun / light_environment - mega-fun _ In order to play this map, you need Rally Race Mod installed in your server. If you want to play this map, you can join FRAGXL.com | Rally RaceMania - 80.172.230.146:27095
